title: ED and CBI free, polls come in between, Govt has no role: PM Narendra Modi - The Indian Express
content: ED and CBI free, polls come in between, Govt has no role: PM Narendra Modi  The Indian ExpressView Full coverage on Google News
description: With voting in five state elections, including UP and Punjab, beginning in phases on Thursday, Modi said: “There is a BJP wave. The BJP will win elections in these five states with a huge majority.”
